Add a `commit_check` MCP tool exposing the deterministic trailer-coverage gate to agents. It returns the exact payload as `decree commit-check --json` (a shared `_payload` formatter guarantees the CLI and MCP tool never diverge): resolve paths from `diff`/`diff_base`/`changed_paths` and trailers from `diff_base` (squash-safe CI mode) or `message` (commit-msg mode), gateable via `strict`/`min_coverage`. Read-only and LLM-free; reads only the authoritative declared `governs:` layer.
